## Installation

1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/smart-health-monitoring.git
   cd smart-health-monitoring
   ```

2. Set up a virtual environment:
   ```bash
   python -m venv venv
   source venv/bin/activate
   ```

3. Install the required packages:
   ```bash
   pip install -r requirements.txt
   ```

4. Configure environment variables for secrets management. Create a `.env` file in the root directory with the following variables:
   ```
   KAFKA_BOOTSTRAP_SERVERS=your_kafka_servers
   REDIS_URL=your_redis_url
   MLFLOW_TRACKING_URI=your_mlflow_uri
   ```

